main event: A UFO sighting involving one disc-shaped blue-white object with red blinking lights observed in Holt, Florida on 25 Jun 55.
interesting points: The sighting lasted between 2 to 10 minutes,The object was reported as being 3 inches in diameter,The area was described as stormy with lightning and haze which complicated the identification of the object,The sighting was evaluated with unreliable witnesses leading to the conclusion of being potentially a balloon or aircraft,Three observers confirmed the sighting.
sighted object: one disc-shaped blue-white object with red blinking lights
